2004-03-09  Moray Allan  <moray@sermisy.org>

	* New version: 1.0.5.

2004-03-08  Philip Blundell  <philb@gnu.org>

	* Makefile: Add dependency tracking gubbins.

	* gsm-codec.c: Include <string.h> to silence warning.

2004-03-08  Moray Allan  <moray@sermisy.org>

	* Makefile: Let CFLAGS etc. be passed in at build time.

2003-07-06  Moray Allan  <moray@sermisy.org>

	* Makefile (install-program), gpe-soundbite.menu,
	gpe-soundbite-record.menu: no longer install old-style menu files.
	* Makefile: Remove legacy GTK1 support.

2003-06-10  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* Makefile: Give appropriate permissions to PNGs we install.

2003-04-01  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* Makefile: Build for GTK2 by default.

2003-03-23  Colin Marquardt  <colin@marquardt-home.de>

	* Makefile (install-program): New name for 'install' ('install' is
	now provided by Makefile.dpkg_ipkg).  
	Use -s option for installing the binary, get rid of the strip call.

2003-03-22  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* Makefile: Now uses CVSBUILD to decide where to look for external
	build helper makefiles.

2003-01-09  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* Makefile: Fix .desktop files to have a .desktop extension when
	installed (lacked any extension previously).
	* gpe-soundbite-play, gpe-soundbite-record: Added scripts to be run
	from the .desktop files, to work with the current mbdesktop which
	doesn't like options on Exec= lines.

2003-01-06  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* main.c: Removed use of GtkMiniFileSelection, in favour of the
	ordinary GtkFileSelection.

2002-12-11  Moray Allan  <moray@handhelds.org>

	* main.c: Add 'stream' option to send audio to stdout.

2002-10-06  Philip Blundell  <philb@gnu.org>

	* main.c: Update paths to libgpewidget headers.
	* Makefile: Support GTK 2 and i18n.  Use Makefile.dpkg_ipkg and
	Makefile.translation.

2002-07-29  Colin Marquardt  <colin@marquardt-home.de>

	* gpe-soundbite.menu: Give full path for icon.

